<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Command Guide - CertiFried Announcer</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/dashboard-style.css?v=11.0.0">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/header') %>
<main class="page-container">
    <div class="page-header">
        <h1><i class="fas fa-book me-2"></i>Command Guide</h1>
        <p>A complete guide to all available slash commands. Permissions are required to use these commands.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-lg-4"><div class="command-category-card h-100"><h4><i class="fas fa-star me-2 text-warning"></i>Core Setup</h4><hr><div class="command-entry"><strong>/setchannel</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p>Sets the default channel for announcements.</p></div><div class="command-entry"><strong>/setliverole</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p>Sets a role for linked users when they go live.</p></div><div class="command-entry"><strong>/customize-bot</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p>Changes the bot's default webhook name/avatar.</p></div><div class="command-entry"><strong>/setup-requests</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-admin">Admin</span><p>Creates a panel for members to request their streams.</p></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-lg-4"><div class="command-category-card h-100"><h4><i class="fas fa-paint-brush me-2"></i>Customization</h4><hr><div class="command-entry"><strong>/customize-streamer</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p>Sets a unique name, avatar, or message for a streamer.</p></div><div class="command-entry"><strong>/customize-channel</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p>Sets a default name/avatar for a specific channel.</p></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-lg-4"><div class="command-category-card h-100"><h4><i class="fas fa-user-plus me-2"></i>Management</h4><hr><div class="command-entry"><strong>/addstreamer</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p>Adds a streamer to the notification list.</p></div><div class="command-entry"><strong>/removestreamer</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p>Removes a streamer from the list.</p></div><div class="command-entry"><strong>/liststreamers</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p>Shows all tracked streamers.</p></div><div class="command-entry"><strong>/check-live</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p>Instantly lists all currently live streamers.</p></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-12"><div class="command-category-card"><h4><i class="fas fa-rocket me-2 text-info"></i>Bulk & Team Actions</h4><hr><div class="row g-4"><div class="col-lg-6"><div class="command-entry"><strong>/addteam</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p>(One-Time) Adds all members of a Twitch Team.</p></div><div class="command-entry"><strong>/removeteam</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p>(One-Time) Removes all members of a Twitch Team.</p></div><div class="command-entry"><strong>/subscribe-team</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p>(Automated) Keeps a channel synced with a Twitch Team.</p></div><div class="command-entry"><strong>/unsubscribe-team</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p>Stops the automatic team sync.</p></div></div><div class="col-lg-6"><div class="command-entry"><strong>/massaddstreamer</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p>Adds a list of streamers from one platform.</p></div><div class="command-entry"><strong>/importcsv</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p>Adds/updates streamers in bulk from a CSV file.</p></div><div class="command-entry"><strong>/exportcsv</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-mod">Moderator</span><p>Exports all tracked streamers to a CSV file.</p></div><div class="command-entry"><strong>/clearstreamers</strong><span class="perm-badge perm-admin">Admin</span><p>Removes **ALL** streamers from the entire server.</p></div></div></div></div></div>
    </div>
</main>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>